Fanny Gautier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fanny_Gautier 0 Fanny Solórzano Gautier (born 21 November 1970, in Madrid, Spain) is a Spanish actress. She is famous for portraying Alicia Jauregi in the Spanish television series Un paso adelante, and in the films Abre los ojos, Elsa y Fred and La Torre de Suso.
